{"lemma":"تَبْلِيغاتٌ","slug":"تَبْلِيغاتٌ","root":"ب.ل.غ","root_slug":"ب-ل-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3223"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%BA%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَلَّغَ (ballaḡa) (form II)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of بَلَّغَ (ballaḡa)."},"ipa":["/tab.liːɣ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3223","headword_ar":"تَبْلِيغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibolaAgN","text_ar":"اـِبْلَاغٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~g","text_ar":"بلّغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablg","text_ar":"ابلغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signify The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causing to reach, attain, arrive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come; bringing, conveying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delivering:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) the former is the more common. (Er-Rághib, TA.) [You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~ghu AlmakaAna","text_ar":"بلّغهُ المَكَانَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He caused him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, to reach, attain, arrive at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come to, the place."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~ghu maqoSuwdahu","text_ar":"بلّغهُ مَقْصُودَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He caused him to attain his object of aim"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavour"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bal~agotu Alr~isaAlapa","text_ar":"بَلَّغْتُ الرِّسَالَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I brought, conveyed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delivered, the message"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~ghu Als~alaAma","text_ar":"بلّغهُ السَّلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxabara","text_ar":"الخَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablghu","text_ar":"ابلغهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought, conveyed, delivered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"communicated, to him the salutation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"told, to him the news,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"information."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bal~aganiY Eano fulaAnK","text_ar":"بَلَّغَنِى عَنْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He told me from such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the part of such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"some piece of information, or that some event had happened, &c.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~g AlfaArisu","text_ar":"بلّغ الفَارِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboliygN","text_ar":"تَبْلِيغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The horseman stretched forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extended, his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm, with the rein of his horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave the rein to his horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that he might increase in his running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~g Al$~ayobu fiY raA^osihi","text_ar":"بلّغ الشَّيْبُ فِى رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hoariness began to appear on his head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to IAar; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bl~E","text_ar":"بلّع"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E","text_ar":"ع"},{"kind":"text","text":": the Basrees assert that the former is a mistranscription; but it is related as heard from Th, by Aboo-Bekr Es-Soolee. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Msb","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}